{"tid":526832,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"琴日行街 無啦啦俾星探截停","createTime":"2018-01-12T04:26:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-13T18:47:28.000Z","uid":25741,"like":828,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"357e9797534f21588a67e618055d82e6e651bdac","tid":526832,"uid":25741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T04:26:41.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n琴日一個人行街無啦啦有個女人迎面截停我<br />\n話佢公司係做雜誌果啲 要揾啲model影相<br />\n我當時呆一呆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊有咁筍<br />\n咁大個仔都未遇過呢啲野 回過神來<br />\n佢已經攞左張卡片想俾我<br />\n心諗咪玩啦 我又無吳彥祖個樣<br />\n又無胡師傅個身材 本身又係個矮撚<br />\n方死唔係要交set頭費 化妝費 培訓費啲fd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我話 唔需要啦唔該 我趕時間<br />\n想轉身就走 佢話俾一分鐘佢<br />\n我善意咁點左個頭表示不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢都未講完 我就頭也不回咁走左<br />\n連佢遞左十幾秒嘅卡片都無攞<br />\n大家真係要小心呢啲<br />\n騙徒手法層出不窮<br />\n專呃啲好有自信嘅毒撚<br />\n定力小小唔夠真係會上當<br />\n以為自己好靚仔有人欣賞<br />\n然後就傾家蕩產發明星夢<br />\n今朝早起身忽然覺得<br />\n琴日好似錯過左人生奔向大好前途嘅機會<br />\n上來係想問下小姐你公司係咩<br />\n琴日我應該攞卡片㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者我今日同樣時間行返果到<br />\n你發掘多我一次得唔得呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14483539147ca7a934e08ddc2700e127a721995a","tid":526832,"uid":2035,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T04:28:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50ed878320803f736fb3cb9b617467516c56b475","tid":526832,"uid":21423,"like":762,"dislike":22,"score":740,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T04:28:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"63a397603fa2bec43e32d2bcc94535243aa25ea5","tid":